										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: inherit;">India Post GDS 2nd Merit List 2026 Date: Result for 28,740 Posts Expected Soon</span></strong></p>
<p>India Post GDS 2nd Merit List 2026: The <strong>India Post Department</strong> is expected to release the <strong>India Post GDS 2nd Merit List 2026</strong> soon on its official website. Candidates who applied for the <strong>Gramin Dak Sevak (GDS) Recruitment 2026</strong> will be able to check their results online at <strong>indiapostgdsonline.gov.in</strong> once the merit list is published.</p>
<p>The second merit list will be released <strong>after the completion of document verification for the first merit list</strong>, which is scheduled to conclude on <strong>23 March 2026</strong>. The result will be published in <strong>PDF format</strong>, containing the names or registration numbers of shortlisted candidates.</p>
<p>Along with the merit list, the department will also release <strong>state-wise cut-off marks and selection details</strong> for the recruitment process.</p>
<p><a href="https://jobapply24.in/india-post-gds-merit-list-2026/">India Post GDS Merit List 2026 Released â€“ Download GDS 1st Merit List</a></p>
