<h3>India Post GDS 2nd Merit List 2026 Date &amp; Time</h3>
<p>The <strong>GDS Result 2026 second merit list</strong> will likely be released <strong>after March 23, 2026</strong>, once the document verification process for candidates selected in the first merit list is completed.</p>
<p>Candidates who applied for <strong>GDS, Branch Post Master (BPM), and Assistant Branch Post Master (ABPM)</strong> posts can check their names in the <strong>merit list PDF available on the official portal</strong>.</p>
<p>The merit list will include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Candidateâ€™s <strong>registration number</strong></li>
<li><strong>Name of shortlisted candidates</strong></li>
<li><strong>Division / state details</strong></li>
