<thead>
<tr>
<th>Document</th>
<th>Status</th>
<th>Action</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>RRB Paramedical Admit Card 2026</td>
<td>Available</td>
<td>Download Now</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Official Website</td>
<td>Active</td>
<td>Visit Portal</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Exam Schedule</td>
<td>Announced</td>
<td>Check Details</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h3>How to Download RRB Paramedical Admit Card 2026</h3>
<h4>RRB Paramedical Admit Card 2026 &#8211; Direct Download Link</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://rrb.digialm.com/EForms/loginAction.do?subAction=ViewLoginPage&amp;formId=98076&amp;orgId=33128" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download Admit Card Now</a></strong></p>
<p>Candidates can follow the steps below to download their hall ticket:</p>
<ol>
<li>Visit the official RRB regional website such as <strong>rrbcdg.gov.in</strong> or the centralized portal <strong>rrb.digialm.com</strong>.</li>
<li>Look for the <strong>â€œCEN 03/2025 â€“ Paramedical Categoriesâ€�</strong> section.</li>
<li>Click on the <strong>RRB Paramedical Admit Card 2026 / E-Call Letter</strong> link.</li>
<li>Enter your login details:
<ul>
<li>Registration Number</li>
<li>Date of Birth (DD/MM/YYYY)</li>
<li>Captcha Code (if required)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Click on the <strong>Submit / Login</strong> button.</li>
<li>Your <strong>RRB Paramedical Admit Card</strong> will appear on the screen.</li>
<li>Download the PDF file.</li>
<li>Take <strong>2â€“3 printouts</strong> for use on the exam day.</li>
</ol>
<h3>Details Mentioned on RRB Paramedical Admit Card</h3>
<p><a href="https://jobapply24.in/rrb-paramedical-exam-date-2026-announced-cen-03-2025-cbt-scheduled-from-march-10-to-12/">RRB Paramedical Exam Date 2026 Announced, CEN 03/2025 CBT Scheduled from March 10 to 12</a></p>
<p>Candidates should verify the following information on the hall ticket:</p>
<ul>
<li>Candidateâ€™s Name</li>
<li>Registration Number</li>
<li>Roll Number</li>
<li>Exam Date and Shift</li>
<li>Reporting Time</li>
<li>Exam Centre Address</li>
<li>Photograph and Signature</li>
<li>Important Exam Instructions</li>
</ul>
<p>If any information is incorrect, candidates should immediately contact the <strong>RRB helpdesk</strong> for correction.</p>
<p><a href="https://jobapply24.in/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_5400.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1296" src="https://jobapply24.in/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_5400.jpeg" alt="RRB Paramedical Admit Card 2026" width="1024" height="572" srcset="https://jobapply24.in/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_5400.jpeg 1024w, https://jobapply24.in/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_5400-300x168.jpeg 300w, https://jobapply24.in/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_5400-768x429.jpeg 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>
<h3>Important Instructions for Candidates</h3>
